2575   1913             ; synopsis: look insIDE a certain DIRECTORY for files/directories
2576   1913             ; BEFORE CALLING THIS FUNCTION, CD INTO REQUIRED DIRECTORY
2577   1913             ; for each entry insIDE DIRECTORY:
2578   1913             ;  if entry is a file:
